com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.data
Class Attribute

java.lang.Object
  com.exacttarget.etpushsdk.data.Attribute
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<Attribute>
public class Attribute
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<Attribute>

Attribute contains a key/value pair. Each push message can contain an optional ArrayList of Attribute objects. You can register on the EventBus for PushReceivedEvent. The payload in PushReceivedEvent contains "keys" that contains an ArrayList of Attribute objects.
